title: Zep Unplugged
content:
Acoustic Tribute to the Music of Led Zeppelin

Catch our shows near you soon, we are playing all over DFW and have plans to expand further out. We feature a mesmerizing multi-media performance with video production. A very visually stimulating show awaits all who desire to come see us.

For more information on the band, visit our website www.zepunplugged.com or visit our Facebook page @zepunplugged

title: Original Music in the Works
content:
A side project of original music is always bouncing around in my head...

Catch a solo acoustic show soon to hear some of the work. This project will consist of a variety of music from acoustic, upbeat blues, twists on some classic rock genres, pop-punk and as always lots of harmonies and stuck-in-your-head "earworm" melodies!

This is ongoing, I hope to have more updates soon as I collaborate with the amazing Steve Junge on this project.

title: Green Dazed
content:
A Texas-sized Tribute to the Music of Green Day

Established in 2016, we have been performing all over the US as a power trio delivering high energy shows and 3 part harmonies, catch a show near you soon!

For more information on the band, visit our Facebook page @greendazed

title: Dallas Boston Xperience - DBX
content:
We are launched and performing all over Texas and further out in the near future. Come check out a show! It's a multi-media event (when video screens are available) and lots of energy!

For more information on the band, visit our website www.dallasbostonxperience.com or visit our Facebook page @dallasbostonxperience
